OL,6,     FJordan v Algeria (Kick-off
OL,7,     F4.00am). Semra Hunter presents
OL,8,     Fcoverage of the Group J match at
OL,9,     FSan Francisco Bay Area Stadium in
OL,10,     Fthe USA, as the two teams meet for
OL,11,     Fjust the fourth time, and a first
OL,12,     Fin 22 years. Jordan finished
OL,13,     Fsecond in AFC third-round
OL,14,     Fqualifying Group B behind South
OL,15,     FKorea to reach their first-ever
OL,16,     FWorld Cup. Four victories and four
OL,17,     Fdraws in 10 games were enough to
OL,18,     Fearn 16 points and finish one
OL,19,     Fpoint clear of Iraq to avoid going
OL,20,     Finto the fourth round of
OL,21,     Fqualifying and confirm their place
OL,22,     Fat these finals. Algeria reached
